</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>If a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>, then it is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001J.xml" title="Sets" addr="forest://erct/erct-001J" type="local">set</fr:link>.</html:p>
